00:45:56.000 --> 00:45:59.120 align:middle line:84%
>> A document reveals that all
of these victims could have

00:45:59.120 --> 00:46:01.004 align:middle line:90%
been spared.

00:46:01.004 --> 00:46:05.210 align:middle line:84%
On May 22, 1984, a
meeting took place

00:46:05.210 --> 00:46:07.220 align:middle line:90%
at the DuPont headquarters.

00:46:07.220 --> 00:46:09.320 align:middle line:84%
The directors are worried
about the consequences

00:46:09.320 --> 00:46:10.850 align:middle line:90%
for the inhabitants.

00:46:10.850 --> 00:46:16.100 align:middle line:84%
They plan to eliminate
all C-8 emissions.

00:46:16.100 --> 00:46:19.360 align:middle line:84%
>> I wanted to show you
these sentences here.

00:46:19.360 --> 00:46:22.280 align:middle line:90%


00:46:22.280 --> 00:46:25.190 align:middle line:84%
>> But finally, no
measures are taken.

00:46:25.190 --> 00:46:31.040 align:middle line:84%
Their argument, it's not
economically attractive.

00:46:31.040 --> 00:46:32.220 align:middle line:90%
>> That was in what year?

00:46:32.220 --> 00:46:34.830 align:middle line:90%
>> '84.

00:46:34.830 --> 00:46:36.270 align:middle line:90%
That's before we were married.

00:46:36.270 --> 00:46:37.280 align:middle line:90%
That's a long time ago.

00:46:37.280 --> 00:46:38.660 align:middle line:90%
>> Uh-huh, yeah.

00:46:38.660 --> 00:46:40.860 align:middle line:90%
>> Long, long time ago.

00:46:40.860 --> 00:46:41.730 align:middle line:90%
>> That's crazy.

00:46:41.730 --> 00:46:44.010 align:middle line:84%
That's what makes
it so bad, you know?

00:46:44.010 --> 00:46:47.610 align:middle line:84%
That they had evidence all
along and just disregarded it

00:46:47.610 --> 00:46:49.350 align:middle line:84%
and kept doing what
they were doing.

00:46:49.350 --> 00:46:53.070 align:middle line:84%
>> It was company greed that
caused this whole situation.

00:46:53.070 --> 00:46:55.380 align:middle line:84%
They knew what they
were doing to us,

00:46:55.380 --> 00:46:58.530 align:middle line:84%
and they continued
to do it for money.

00:46:58.530 --> 00:47:03.210 align:middle line:84%
That's the only reason
they continued to do it.

00:47:03.210 --> 00:47:05.640 align:middle line:84%
>> DuPont refuses to
collectively compensate

00:47:05.640 --> 00:47:08.610 align:middle line:90%
the 3,500 sick people.

